snippet.title: Guitar Hero III: Legends of Rock Trailer featuring SLASH
snippet.description:
Guitar Hero III: Legends of Rock featuring: SLASH!

Heroes never die, but LEGENDS LIVE FOREVER!

Guitar Hero III: Legends of Rock.  Coming this October to the Wii, Xbox 360, PS3 and PS2!
